The anion-exchange route is an indirect synthesis route as the used precursor in this technique is the LDH that has robust anion-exchange characteristics. The facility of monovalent ions exchange is arranged as follows: NO3−\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
